Usage: check_syntax [-help] [file1.tcl file2.tcl ...] [<nagelfar.tcl options>] [-options] [-out_file <file>]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<file1.tcl file2.tcl ...>       # Files need to check (string, optional)
<nagelfar.tcl options>          # nagelfar.tcl options (string, optional)
-options                        # List out all the legal nagelfar options (bool, optional)
-out_file <file>                # Send the output to file, rather than the default of stdout (string, optional)